Dear {!Case.Lease_Payment__c},
Thank you for choosing SunPower!
To set up your account for automatic payment, please fill out the attached ACH Authorization Agreement form (Exhibit F) and email it to booking@sunpower.com. Please include a scanned copy of a voided check. Alternatively you may fax to the attention of Billing Department, Fax# (512) 684-0288.
If you require more information, please feel free to call 1-800-SUNPOWER or send us an email at billing@sunpower.com.
Billing office hours: 8:00AM-5:00AM PST, Monday Friday.
Sincerely,
Your SunPower Customer Care Department
